<section id="tools">
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1054D" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW"><link href="text/shared/explorer/database/menutools.xhp">Tools</link></paragraph>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1055D" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">The Tools menu of a database window.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10560" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Relationships<comment>or Relation Design (spec has both)</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10576" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens the <link href="text/shared/explorer/database/05020000.xhp">Relation Design</link> view and checks whether the database connection supports relations.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1058A" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">User Administration</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1058E" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens the User Administration dialog.<comment>UFI: where is this specced?</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN105A3" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Table Filter</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105A7" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens the Table Filter dialog, where you specify which tables of the database shall be visible or hidden.<comment>see text in shared\explorer\database\11090000.xhp</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN105BC" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Execute SQL</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN105C0" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW">Opens the SQL dialog where you can enter SQL statements.<comment>UFI: may be shared\02\14030000.xhp</comment></paragraph>
</body>
